title: Fear Factory - Genexus [Limited Edition](2015)320ak
description:
Genexus is the upcoming ninth studio album by American heavy metal band Fear Factory, set to be released on August 7, 2015.[1][2] This will be the third studio album from Fear Factory since guitarist Dino Cazares rejoined the band in 2009, and their first to feature drummer Mike Heller.[3] Genexus will also be Fear Factory's first release through Nuclear Blast.

Regarding the drums on Genexus, Burton C. A lyric video for the song "ProtoMech" was released on July 11.A lyric video for the song "Dielectric" was released on July 30.[5]

Touring

Between the end of August and the middle of September in 2015, the ensemble has plans to tour the southern, midwestern and southwestern United States along with Once Human (featuring Logan Mader), Los Angeles metal band Before the Mourning and Chicago rock/metal band The Bloodline.[7]
